WEBVTT

00:00.300 --> 00:03.934
Quorum — the Nonprofit Board OS.

00:04.234 --> 00:12.932
Who's signed — and who hasn't? The portal answers that everywhere you look. Let's start
on the Dashboard.

00:13.232 --> 00:23.202
The Awaiting signature card counts documents still out with the board. One, right now.
Let's click Documents to see which one.

00:23.502 --> 00:34.432
In the library, read the Status column. The Bylaws say Awaiting signatures — and right
underneath, in small print: three of seven board members signed.

00:34.732 --> 00:42.758
Open the document for the full picture: a progress bar, and a green Signed check beside
every name that's already done.

00:43.058 --> 00:51.732
For anyone still pending, the Remind button sends a friendly nudge — just to them. No
group guilt-trips required.

00:52.032 --> 01:04.570
And when everyone's in, the badge turns green — Fully signed — like our Organizational
Board Minutes here. Nothing left to chase. Next up: creating a motion.
